Third-party components
----------------------
Audio rendering is provided by libopenmpt (https://lib.openmpt.org/), which is
distributed under the BSD 3-Clause license. On Windows the libopenmpt DLLs are
bundled in xmwav/libs/; their license text is in xmwav/libs/LICENSE.libopenmpt.txt.
On macOS and Linux libopenmpt is used from the system package.
